the bye bye man is a 2017 american supernatural horror film directed by stacy title and written by jonathan penner , based on the chapter " the bridge to body island " in robert damon schneck 's book the president 's vampire .   the film stars douglas smith , lucien laviscount , cressida bonas , doug jones , carrie-anne moss , faye dunaway and jenna kanell .   principal photography began on november 2 , 2015 , in cleveland , ohio .   stx entertainment released the film on january 13 , 2017 , received negative reviews however the film was a box office success grossing $ 26 million worldwide on a budget of $ 7.4 million .